---
title: Tasty Beef & Pork Cheeseburger with Fries, Truffle Mayo & Caramelised Bacon
description: Everyone loves a cheeseburger, so we’re offering up one of our own. The spiced beef and pork patties get cheesy when cooked with melted tasty Totara cheese on the top and served with golden fries with truffle mayo for dipping. It’s a much-loved dish for a reason!
